&lt;BaseLayout title="Dice Notation - RANDSUM" description="Complete guide to
RANDSUM dice notation syntax and modifiers"&gt; &lt;div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto
px-4 py-8"&gt; &lt;!-- Header --&gt; &lt;div class="mb-12"&gt; &lt;h1
class="text-4xl font-bold text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt; RANDSUM Dice Notation
&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p class="text-xl text-silver-300 leading-relaxed"&gt; A
comprehensive guide to RANDSUM's powerful dice notation syntax and modifiers
&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;!-- Overview --&gt; &lt;section class="mb-12"&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-silver-50 mb-6"&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none"&gt; &lt;p class="text-silver-300
leading-relaxed mb-4"&gt; Dice notation is a compact way to represent dice rolls
and their modifications. For example, &lt;code class="bg-randsum-800 px-2 py-1
rounded text-silver-100"&gt;4d20+2&lt;/code&gt; means "roll four twenty-sided
dice, then add two". &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="text-silver-300
leading-relaxed"&gt; RANDSUM extends standard dice notation with powerful
modifiers like dropping lowest rolls, rerolling specific values, and ensuring
unique results. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/section&gt; &lt;!-- Basic Syntax
--&gt; &lt;section class="mb-12"&gt; &lt;h2 class="text-2xl font-bold
text-silver-50 mb-6"&gt;Basic Syntax&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;div class="bg-randsum-800
p-4 rounded-lg mb-6"&gt; &lt;p class="text-silver-300"&gt; All notation in
RANDSUM is case-insensitive (&lt;code
class="text-silver-100"&gt;2d8&lt;/code&gt; = &lt;code
class="text-silver-100"&gt;2D8&lt;/code&gt;). &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;h3
class="text-xl font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt;Standard Rolls&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="bg-randsum-900 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6"&gt; &lt;pre
class="text-silver-100 overflow-x-auto"&gt;&lt;code&gt;// Roll one d20 roll(20)
// number argument roll('1d20') // notation string roll(&#123; sides: 20,
quantity: 1 &#125;) // Roll four d6 roll('4d6') roll(&#123; sides: 6, quantity:
4 &#125;)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;h3 class="text-xl
font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt;Custom-Faced Dice&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p
class="text-silver-300 mb-4"&gt;Roll dice with non-numeric faces:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="bg-randsum-900 rounded-lg p-6 mb-4"&gt; &lt;pre
class="text-silver-100 overflow-x-auto"&gt;&lt;code&gt;// Roll a coin
(heads/tails) four times import &#123; rollCustomFaces &#125; from
'@randsum/dice' rollCustomFaces('4d&#123;HT&#125;') rollCustomFaces(&#123;
sides: ['H', 'T'], quantity: 4 &#125;) // Roll Fudge/Fate dice
rollCustomFaces('4d&#123;++-- &#125;') // Plus, minus, blank faces
rollCustomFaces(&#123; sides: ['+', '+', '-', '-', ' ', ' '], quantity: 4
&#125;)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="bg-amber-900/20
border border-amber-600/30 rounded-lg p-4"&gt; &lt;p class="text-amber-200"&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; Custom-faced dice ignore modifiers and always
return a total of 0. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/section&gt; &lt;!-- Modifiers
--&gt; &lt;section class="mb-12"&gt; &lt;h2 class="text-2xl font-bold
text-silver-50 mb-6"&gt;Modifiers&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;h3 class="text-xl font-semibold
text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt;Basic Arithmetic&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;div
class="bg-randsum-900 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6"&gt; &lt;pre class="text-silver-100
overflow-x-auto"&gt;&lt;code&gt;roll('4d6+2') // Add 2 to total roll(&#123;
sides: 6, quantity: 4, modifiers: &#123; plus: 2 &#125; &#125;) roll('4d6-1') //
Subtract 1 from total roll(&#123; sides: 6, quantity: 4, modifiers: &#123;
minus: 1 &#125; &#125;)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;h3
class="text-xl font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt;Cap Modifiers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class="text-silver-300 mb-4"&gt;Limit roll values to specific
ranges:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="bg-randsum-900 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6"&gt; &lt;pre
class="text-silver-100
overflow-x-auto"&gt;&lt;code&gt;roll('4d20C&#123;&gt;18&#125;') // Cap rolls
over 18 to 18 roll(&#123; sides: 20, quantity: 4, modifiers: &#123; cap: &#123;
greaterThan: 18 &#125; &#125; &#125;) roll('4d20C&#123;&lt;3&#125;') // Cap
rolls under 3 to 3 roll(&#123; sides: 20, quantity: 4, modifiers: &#123; cap:
&#123; lessThan: 3 &#125; &#125; &#125;) roll('4d20C&#123;&lt;2,&gt;19&#125;')
// Cap rolls under 2 to 2 and over 19 to 19&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; &lt;h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt;Drop
Modifiers&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p class="text-silver-300 mb-4"&gt;Drop specific dice
from the results:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="bg-randsum-900 rounded-lg p-6
mb-6"&gt; &lt;pre class="text-silver-100
overflow-x-auto"&gt;&lt;code&gt;roll('4d6L') // Drop lowest roll(&#123; sides:
6, quantity: 4, modifiers: &#123; drop: &#123; lowest: 1 &#125; &#125; &#125;)
roll('4d6L2') // Drop 2 lowest roll('4d6H') // Drop highest roll('4d6H2') //
Drop 2 highest // Drop by value roll('4d20D&#123;&gt;17&#125;') // Drop rolls
over 17 roll('4d20D&#123;&lt;5&#125;') // Drop rolls under 5
roll('4d20D&#123;8,12&#125;') // Drop 8s and 12s&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; &lt;h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt;Reroll
Modifiers&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p class="text-silver-300 mb-4"&gt;Reroll dice matching
certain conditions:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="bg-randsum-900 rounded-lg p-6
mb-6"&gt; &lt;pre class="text-silver-100
overflow-x-auto"&gt;&lt;code&gt;roll('4d20R&#123;&gt;17&#125;') // Reroll
results over 17 roll('4d20R&#123;&lt;5&#125;') // Reroll results under 5
roll('4d20R&#123;8,12&#125;') // Reroll 8s and 12s
roll('4d20R&#123;&lt;5&#125;3') // Reroll under 5, max 3
attempts&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;h3 class="text-xl
font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt;Exploding Dice&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p
class="text-silver-300 mb-4"&gt;Reroll and add when maximum value is
rolled:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="bg-randsum-900 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6"&gt; &lt;pre
class="text-silver-100 overflow-x-auto"&gt;&lt;code&gt;roll('4d6!') // Explode
on 6s roll('4d10!') // Explode on 10s roll('4d20!') // Explode on
20s&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;h3 class="text-xl font-semibold
text-silver-50 mb-4"&gt;Unique Results&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p class="text-silver-300
mb-4"&gt;Ensure all dice show different values:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div
class="bg-randsum-900 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6"&gt; &lt;pre class="text-silver-100
overflow-x-auto"&gt;&lt;code&gt;roll('4d20U') // All different results
roll('5d6U') // All different results (if possible)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/section&gt; &lt;!-- Common Examples --&gt; &lt;section
class="mb-12"&gt; &lt;h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-silver-50
mb-6"&gt;Common Examples&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;div class="grid grid-cols-1
md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"&gt; &lt;div class="bg-randsum-800 rounded-lg p-6"&gt;
&lt;h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-3"&gt;D&D Ability
Scores&lt;/h4&gt; &lt;code class="text-silver-100"&gt;4d6L&lt;/code&gt; &lt;p
class="text-silver-300 text-sm mt-2"&gt;Roll 4d6, drop lowest&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="bg-randsum-800 rounded-lg p-6"&gt; &lt;h4
class="text-lg font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-3"&gt;D&D Advantage&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;code class="text-silver-100"&gt;2d20H&lt;/code&gt; &lt;p
class="text-silver-300 text-sm mt-2"&gt;Roll 2d20, keep highest&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="bg-randsum-800 rounded-lg p-6"&gt; &lt;h4
class="text-lg font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-3"&gt;Damage +
Modifier&lt;/h4&gt; &lt;code class="text-silver-100"&gt;1d8+3&lt;/code&gt; &lt;p
class="text-silver-300 text-sm mt-2"&gt;Roll 1d8, add 3&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="bg-randsum-800 rounded-lg p-6"&gt; &lt;h4 class="text-lg
font-semibold text-silver-50 mb-3"&gt;Exploding Damage&lt;/h4&gt; &lt;code
class="text-silver-100"&gt;2d6!&lt;/code&gt; &lt;p class="text-silver-300
text-sm mt-2"&gt;Roll 2d6, explode on 6s&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt; &lt;!-- Navigation --&gt; &lt;div class="flex justify-between
